title: Sachi To Yuuka
alternative_title: サチとユーカ ; Sachi and Yuuka
status: サチとユーカ ; Sachi and Yuuka
description:
Description :
        Sachi and Yuka, friends from college, are housemates and partners. Yuka, who is free-spirited, and Sachi, who tends to underestimate herself. A romantic comedy of two working adults who have opposite personalities.
